::Koj/EndBringer::

Koj yelps in surprise, flying forward into EndBringer and Killfest 
when five shots (the four plus the previous one) hit him in the back. 
He clenches his teeth when EndBringer's tentacles wrap around him and 
start electricuting, smoke rising from Koj's circuits.
